&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Raag Kalyan&lt;/strong&gt;: It is also known as Raag Yaman.&amp;nbsp;In thaat Kalyan, all notes are shuddha (natural) except teevra (sharp) Ma.&lt;/li&gt;
